headline: Why Waters Corporation (WAT) Stock Is Up Today
summary: Shares of scientific instruments company Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) jumped 3.2% in the morning session after Rothschild & Co initiated coverage on the stock with a 'Buy' rating and a $390 price target.
